title: Hawkwind friends & relations volume 3 lyrics
description:
And here is the torrent with the lyrics, as promissed some time later. That is, when the captcha is showing up as it should, 5 minutes. It goes with the album that I think inspired the name of the album rareties, as on volume 3 there are a few things you won't find anywhere but here. 
The lyrics are not complete, so if there is anyone out there that can be of any assistence, do not hesitate. 

I won't give you any kisses, but you do get my love and I will have a beer on that with you in my mind.

And else I have a beer anyway.

Have a nice dahay!

Umuzungu
